A 0.5 255,255,255
C -100,0,0 1,0,0 120
L 3,3,3 0.5 200,200,200

# Expected:
# - A full grid of spheres in the Y–Z plane at x=10 (like graph paper).
# - Center (y=0,z=0) is RED.
# - +Y axis is GREEN, -Y axis is BLUE.
# - +Z axis is CYAN, -Z axis is YELLOW.
# If the colors appear on the wrong sides, your Y/Z sign or axis mapping is wrong.
# If you can’t see the full ±120 range with FOV 160, move the grid farther (e.g. x=30)
# or move camera back; the file is still correct.

